-> Extract ONLY those critical sentences verbatim from the text. 
-> Combine them into a single string for the "parameter_value" field. 
-> Keep parameter value concise and short (2 sentences only).
-> Do NOT rewrite or summarize in your own words.

Important:
parameter_name = lowest-level section name  
parameter_value = key verbatim statistical planning statements merged into one string  

Both must be exact text from the provided extracted content.

